title: Kubernetes: Node Count
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the number of worker and control plane nodes in a
 kubernetes cluster.
 Upper and lower levels for worker nodes and control plane nodes are
 configurable via WATO.
 By default, no levels are set. Thus, the check is always OK.

 The check requires that the special agent kube is configured.

discovery:
 One service is created.
